'''INSANE''' is a proprietary '''IN'''teractive '''S'''treaming '''AN'''imation '''E'''ngine developed by [[LucasArts]].

It greatly compresses moving images so that high quality full-screen videos can be displayed even in hi-res graphics modes on the PC.

It was first used in ''[[Star Wars: Rebel Assault II: The Hidden Empire]]'' and then [[Wikipedia:Full Throttle|''Full Throttle'']], [[Wikipedia:Curse of Monkey Island|''Curse of Monkey Island'']], [[Wikipedia:The Dig|''The Dig'']], and [[Wikipedia:Outlaws (computer game)|''Outlaws'']].<ref>''Outlaws'' press release, as archived [http://www.thecomputershow.com/computershow/previews/outlaws.htm here] (under "Company Line")</ref>

